{"tid":945505,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【老大哥】英警倫敦測試面孔辨識技術　私隱組織斥「獨裁、危險、無法無天」","createTime":"2018-12-18T03:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T03:08:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a59d9620ea0df5fe53bd5ab785b08705294e634a","tid":945505,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:01:28.000Z","msg":"英國警方將於倫敦中部市民忙於聖誕購物時，進行面孔辨識科技測試。《BBC》報道，測試將於本周一和周二於倫敦中部蘇豪區、購物區皮卡迪利圓環（Piccadilly Circus）廣場以及萊斯特廣場（Leicester Square）進行。倫敦警察廳稱，辨識科技可幫助警方認出被通緝人士，穿著制服的警員會進行測試，並向公眾派發傳單，又指會邀請市民參與測試，不會秘密掃描，若有市民不願意而拒絕的話，不會被視為可疑份子。<br />\n<br />\n私隱權益監察組織「老大哥在看著你」（Big Brother Watch）發聲明，批評使用辨識科技在公眾地方監察平民，是「獨裁、危險和無法無天」（authoritarian, dangerous and lawless），侵犯市民私隱、言論自由和集會自由這些基本權利。該組織今年年初曾調查，認為這科技會令大量無辜市民被誤當罪犯。<br />\n<br />\n英國資訊專員(Information Commissioner）Elizabeth Denham，去年在博客中稱面孔辨識科技，會為公眾安全帶來「極大好處」。不過她亦承認，面孔辨識科技會侵犯個人私隱。<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E8%80%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%93%A5-%E8%8B%B1%E8%AD%A6%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E9%9D%A2%E5%AD%94%E8%BE%A8%E8%AD%98%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93-%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E6%96%A5-%E7%8D%A8%E8%A3%81-%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA-%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E7%84%A1%E5%A4%A9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2593%25A5-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2580%25AB%25E6%2595%25A6%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%25AD%2594%25E8%25BE%25A8%25E8%25AD%2598%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E9%259A%25B1%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E6%2596%25A5-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E8%25A3%2581-%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%259A%25AA-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25A4%25A9%2F&d=IZf6lr%2BCsfQX4MnErcdNIcKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=52503779\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2593%25A5-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2580%25AB%25E6%2595%25A6%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E9%259D%25A2%25E5%25AD%2594%25E8%25BE%25A8%25E8%25AD%2598%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593-%25E7%25A7%2581%25E9%259A%25B1%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E6%2596%25A5-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E8%25A3%2581-%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%259A%25AA-%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%25A4%25A9%2F&h=78cf4a92\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E8%80%81%E5%A4%A7%E5%93%A5-%E8%8B%B1%E8%AD%A6%E5%80%AB%E6%95%A6%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E9%9D%A2%E5%AD%94%E8%BE%A8%E8%AD%98%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93-%E7%A7%81%E9%9A%B1%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E6%96%A5-%E7%8D%A8%E8%A3%81-%E5%8D%B1%E9%9A%AA-%E7%84%A1%E6%B3%95%E7%84%A1%E5%A4%A9/</a>"},{"pid":"9ea48858dad688bb42dc666ec2a999fc4aa7bdb9","tid":945505,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:05:27.000Z","msg":"Big brother is watching you"},{"pid":"bd1205576eefcfba4945450fcf800a2a52aa65cf","tid":945505,"uid":72757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:08:51.000Z","msg":"張學友演唱會"}]}